>Warm Regards,</div><div><a href="https://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-uphttps://weclouddata.com/corporate-training/?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=canada-finance-follow-up" target="_blank">WeCloudData</a></div>') ON CONFLICT (campaign_id, step_index, variant_index) DO NOTHING;
